<i>Spin it!</i>

00:04.792 --> 00:06.375
<i>♪ Hoo-hoo-hoo</i>
<i>Hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo ♪</i>

00:06.458 --> 00:07.417
<i>♪ Hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo ♪</i>

